<li sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="17">Vyberte ikonu <img src="media/ui-search/search_small.png" sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="17" alt="Žárovky, která otevře funkci Řekněte mi" title="Řekněte mi, co chcete dělat">, zadejte <strong sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="17">Šablony evidence pošty</strong> a poté vyberte související odkaz.</li>
</ul>
<p sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="19">Na stránce <strong sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="19">Šablony evidence pošty</strong> je třeba vytvořit šablony pro <strong sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="19">Typy pošty</strong> - Odeslaná a Došlá pošta. Dále je možno zaškrtnout, jestli se má <strong sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="19">Kontrolovat číslo externího dokladu</strong>, <strong sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="19">Otevřít kartu dokladu po vytvoření</strong>, <strong sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="19">Pouze jeden doklad</strong>, <strong sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="19">Vytvořit došlý doklad</strong>, <strong sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="19">Přenášet dimenze do dokladu</strong>.</p>
<p sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="21"><img src="media/IM-layout.png" sourcefile="AC-ProductivityPack/ac-incoming-mail-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="21" alt="Nastavení šablony"></p>
